Package: geokit
Title: Tools for Accessing and Working with the Gene Expression Omnibus (GEO)
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Yun", "Peng", , "yunyunpp96@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a tidy and convenient R interface to the NCBI Gene
    Expression Omnibus (GEO) database. Functions are included to query,
    download, and parse GEO metadata and expression data, making it easier to
    integrate GEO datasets into downstream analyses and workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
